Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:13.42,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,对于春天搬到这里来的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:17.23,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,还是一切都很新鲜的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:21.62,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,经历了初次潜水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:26.21,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,拿到开放水域潜水员资格证的第一个夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:32.67,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,现在 我重要的朋友第一次过来玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:43.76,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26.667}つま先からちょっとずつ生まれ変わってく気分　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:43.76,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,有一种由脚尖开始 慢慢重生的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:50.72,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26.667}名前はまだない  始まった物语　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:50.72,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,故事才刚开始 还没有标题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:01:00.88,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26.667}最初の1ページには  风の中に立つ人が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:01:00.88,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的一页上 是谁迎风站立
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:14.32,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26.667}ああ　夏草の匂い　湿った空気と　打ち寄せる波の音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:14.32,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 夏草的清香 湿润的空气 拍岸的海浪声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.12,0:01:27.60,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26.667}ああ　この海が何とつながってるのか　考えているの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.12,0:01:27.60,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我不禁思考 这片大海究竟与何相连
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:36.76,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26.667}今しかできないことをすぐにやらなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:36.76,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,只有现在能的事 必须立刻行动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:42.84,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26.667}几千の云をかき分けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:42.84,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,拨开万千的云层
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:46.20,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26.667}駆け上がる気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:46.20,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,不断攀升的情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:51.40,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26.667}こんな私がいたなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:51.40,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,原来还有这样的我存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:59.52,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26.667}始まった物语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:59.52,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,故事对刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:13.56,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26.667}最初の1ページには　风の中に立つ私がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:13.56,Amanchu_Main,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的一页上有我迎风站立
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:18.84,Amanchu_Ep_Title (S2 Ep13),OP Card,0,0,0,,{\fn@宋体\frz269.5\pos(796.333,576.667)}约定的夏日与新回忆的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:23.54,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,叫什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:26.57,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,那个新朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:29.48,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,记得是叫小日向光...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:32.36,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,她有没有跟人搞好关系啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:35.65,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,不是最后也没能混熟在失落吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:39.36,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,之前打电话的时候 听着挺精神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:44.29,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,有可能是为了不让我们担心而装作精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:49.14,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,真是的...给我等着 双叶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:52.75,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,嗯 她一定等很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.93,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,和我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:01.26,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,千鹤 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:02.55,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,双叶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:04.18,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.58,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,不要慢吞吞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.48,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:08.35,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:10.81,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,过得还好吗？二位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.71,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,那当然是很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:16.26,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,你才是 过得怎么样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:21.99,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,我们担心你在新环境里会不会留下痛苦的回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.50,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,嗯 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:31.97,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,是吗？那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.57,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,谢谢你们担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.56,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,我也想见见那个叫小日向的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.75,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:40.03,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,喂 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:43.90,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,那种事再过会儿慢慢说比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:47.02,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,对啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:50.82,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,双叶 不想说的事可以不说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:53.26,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,但不用跟我们客气的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:54.97,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,任何事都可以跟我们商量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:56.99,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.24,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:12.37,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,我是小日向光 人称闪光 请多光照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:17.80,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,就是这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:21.55,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,在这边学校交到的朋友闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.85,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,和她的奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:25.93,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,我一直在受她们照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:30.23,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,今天的导游就尽管交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:33.69,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,我很期待 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:34.89,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,请多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:38.41,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,我才是 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.60,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,这位是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:41.61,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,是茶顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:43.86,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,茶鼓...纹？？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.47,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,是茶 顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:50.04,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,你们俩是千鹤和小茜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.21,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,我经常听说你们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:53.08,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:56.17,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,你们过来玩我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:59.01,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,毕竟我们约好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:02.01,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,我们打算在这两天里尽情玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:05.01,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,嗯 尽情享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.22,Amanchu_Main,W,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:11.28,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,好大!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:13.62,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,这是令人惊讶的珍品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.23,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,这个炸虾竟然...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:18.32,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,从头到尾都是满满的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:21.53,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,没有用外壳来糊弄长度和粗细
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:29.08,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,超好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:30.70,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:32.30,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,这可真是棒...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:34.00,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,味噌汤是螃蟹的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.92,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,伊豆真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:38.29,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:41.28,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,不 没什么···
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:44.57,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,我还是说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:48.38,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,不过 不要笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.53,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,不会笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.36,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:57.11,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,那个 过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:06:00.82,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,我曾与小茜和千鹤一同度过...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:05.11,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,现在 我与闪光一同度过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:09.16,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,我分别有和你们度过的两段时间...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:13.76,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,虽然这是两件不同的事 但对我来说是非常宝贵的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.77,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,像这样子汇聚在了一起了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:19.88,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,对此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:23.84,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,有种奇妙的难为情的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:27.66,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,我似乎能明白那种感觉 小点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:28.59,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.28,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,小点?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:32.54,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,不过太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:39.42,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,不知道闪光能不能和她们俩搞好关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:41.63,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.73,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,毕竟是小点的朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:56.03,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,双叶看来处得挺好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:58.10,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:02.04,Amanchu_Main,Ki,0,0,0,,好 到了 接下来是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:05.22,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,是城崎海岸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:07.88,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,不不 这与其说是海岸不如说是悬崖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.43,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,岩石凹凸不平...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:13.35,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,意外很...难走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:23.36,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,有种出乎意料的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:30.50,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,本来想着以你来说肯定适应不了新环境会觉得寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:37.70,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,感觉过寂寞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:44.77,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,跟你们俩分开 寂寞得像是世界末日来临了一样...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:46.88,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,双叶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:50.59,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,但是呢 我遇到了闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.88,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,在这里也找到了容身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:58.05,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,全部都是多亏了闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:01.24,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,太好了呢 双叶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:05.19,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,那么 已经不用再担心双叶了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:06.83,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:12.35,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,果然很难掌握平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:15.33,Amanchu_Main,Ki,0,0,0,,玩得开心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:19.26,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,嗯 全是头一次见到的东西 令我很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:21.30,Amanchu_Main,Ki,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:26.88,Amanchu_Main,Ki,0,0,0,,对头一次走的道路会有不安或惊讶等等各种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.72,Amanchu_Main,Ki,0,0,0,,但不要慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.61,Amanchu_Main,Ki,0,0,0,,慢慢来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:34.81,Amanchu_Main,Ki,0,0,0,,然后能开心就算赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:36.95,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.72,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,接下来是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:44.02,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,好高 好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.44,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,好可怕 可怕可怕 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:03.32,Haiku_08:58(Ep 13),SignLBlue,0,0,0,,{\frz347.3\pos(589.667,117)}扛过风雪才会绽放花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:03.32,Please_call_08:58(Ep 13),SignDBlue,0,0,0,,{\pos(376.667,270)\frz347}不来和我商量一下吗  生命求助热线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:07.84,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,果然难度都太高了啊 伊豆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.22,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,那个 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:14.18,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,千鹤 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:17.04,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,想体验下潜水吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.51,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,体验...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:20.05,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,潜水?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:24.79,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,我们社团活动的老师有指导员资格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.43,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,可以带我们去...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:28.44,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:31.25,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,是闪光提议的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:35.78,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,非常想去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:37.77,Amanchu_Main,PT,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:40.04,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,那我给真斗老师打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:43.15,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,哇 潜水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:47.38,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,说起来 双叶之前发来邮件的时候潜水了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:51.38,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,嗯 在那一天拿到了C卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.43,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,C卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:57.70,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,是开放水域潜水员这个资格的证书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:00.56,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,可以不跟着指导员就潜水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:04.02,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.19,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,要晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.15,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:25.36,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,哎呀？明明我想说谢谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.60,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:30.43,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,有点儿头晕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:31.71,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,闪光也没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:34.26,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:36.76,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.59,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:40.32,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,对不起 我是闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.30,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,什么啊是恶作剧电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:43.10,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:47.89,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,小点的朋友想要体验潜水...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:52.14,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,怎么？这心情是什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.44,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.19,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,知道哪个是洗发水吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:00.95,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:12.29,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,果然双叶也很喜欢这张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:15.16,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,真令人怀念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.11,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.64,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,你还一如既往地拍一堆照片吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:28.81,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,那个电子相框 是潜水部的大家给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:31.53,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,是我的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.02,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:45.93,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:49.13,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,没事吗？累了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:54.94,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:03.84,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,感觉像是夜晚的黑暗进入胸中一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:06.14,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,黑暗沉重的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:09.15,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,如鲠在喉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:12.60,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,从刚才一直有的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:16.19,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,感觉我不该察觉它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:19.03,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,我赶忙停止了思考
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:41.01,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,好 那么我来对体验潜水进行说明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:41.70,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.68,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.60,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,没事的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:50.24,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,体验潜水非常安全 所以不会游泳也能潜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:53.76,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,那么 首先 填这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.47,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:58.29,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,病历书和知情书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:01.74,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,还有身高体重脚长等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:03.93,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,体重也要！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:07.62,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,还有 以防万一之时的联系人和承诺书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.50,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,万一...？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:13.24,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,没事的 有我跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:14.25,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,双叶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:18.38,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,没错 有3名潜水员一起潜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:21.08,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,会彻底辅助你们的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.84,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,那个...谢谢 闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:31.10,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,为我的朋友做了许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:34.56,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,不不 我才是享受其中的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:39.74,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,我一定要让那两个人也享受到大海的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:42.78,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,嗯 全力让她们享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:47.48,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,那么 在我们准备好之前稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:48.29,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.28,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,你们那边怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.47,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,气瓶搬完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:53.25,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,接下来是BCD
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.75,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,好 老师我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:57.25,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:13:59.69,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:02.05,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,是说双叶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:02.96,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:06.83,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,之前更犹豫不决战战兢兢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:10.66,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,感觉总是粘在我们后面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:14.16,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,嗯 感觉变好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.01,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,真卖力啊 小点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:17.15,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:21.79,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,千鹤 难道你觉得寂寞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:24.79,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,别说傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:32.22,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,耳压平衡和清除镜面积水没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.12,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.51,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,总之先记住那些就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:37.33,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.96,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,那么让我们潜水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:47.60,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,小点跟着小茜 我来辅助千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:48.43,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:53.51,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,在这里穿上脚蹼吧1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:54.43,Amanchu_Main,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:57.44,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,昨天谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:00.94,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,别在意 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:04.44,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,好 千鹤 穿好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:06.03,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,谢谢...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:10.82,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,你为什么管双叶叫小点呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:16.65,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,因为眉毛淡得就像两个点一样所以取名小点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:20.01,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,原来如此非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:22.62,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,是吧是吧 我起的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:26.99,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,请横着慢慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:30.88,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,冷静下来静静呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.72,Amanchu_Main,Ma,0,0,0,,不要离开搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.08,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,小点？那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:41.61,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,明明双叶有着“双叶”这么好的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:47.41,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,却因为奇怪的理由被起了“小点”这个奇怪的绰号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:04.25,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:07.32,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,怎么回事 这个压迫感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:10.04,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,感觉是有钻头在钻耳朵一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:13.58,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,等等 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.43,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.86,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,好疼 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:20.24,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:30.18,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,耳朵 耳朵好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:33.50,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.94,Equalized_ears_16:32(Ep 13),Sign,0,0,0,,{\frz17.53}耳压平衡了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:39.36,Amanchu_Main,Sign,0,0,0,,耳压平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.54,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:45.89,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,不疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:49.84,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:51.40,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,就像是假的一样 不疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:57.29,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,那两个人都到那么远了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.49,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,糟糕 得赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.10,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,咦? 奇怪！？等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:03.98,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,身体自己翻过来了...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:06.23,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,什么？不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.21,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,我之前不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:04.48,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,曾经以为大海中只是一片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.98,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,没想到还有这么闪闪发光的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:11.62,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:17.08,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,这也只是因为我不知道大海真正的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:28.98,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,超漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:30.92,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,不可怕吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:35.31,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,虽然最开始有点儿害怕 但因为有双叶跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:37.95,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,千鹤也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:40.91,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,超级疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.62,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,还有大家也都先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.01,0:18:48.31,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,身体自己翻过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:51.09,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,那时候感觉接近死亡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.84,Amanchu_Main,Aka,0,0,0,,千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:58.96,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:02.72,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,你最早察觉到了我的状态...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:06.50,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,牵着我的手带我到了大家那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:14.19,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,在耳痛地狱之后看到的大海中的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:16.63,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,有点儿像是天国一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.69,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,都是多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.28,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:29.67,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,还以为我又干了些什么被人讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:30.33,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,我讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:34.47,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,本来是打算这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:44.58,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,一阵子没见的双叶变成了我不认识的双叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:48.98,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,然后就总感觉是你把双叶抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.18,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,我很讨厌这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:51.96,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:55.69,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,闪光是个超级棒的家伙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:58.78,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,话说 那个 我察觉到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:06.60,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,那如鲠在喉的感觉 就算讨厌闪光也不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.25,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:15.51,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,只是我不知道而已 现在的双叶也是双叶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.46,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,千鹤...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:23.12,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,与大家一同度过的伊豆时光 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:25.05,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,谢谢闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:30.94,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,我才是 谢谢你过来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:45.37,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:47.25,Amanchu_Main,Bo,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:58.27,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,要再来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:03.93,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,绝对绝对要再来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:05.68,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,闪光...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:09.06,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,就算你不叫我们也会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:11.74,Amanchu_Main,Chi,0,0,0,,在那之前“小点”就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:14.93,Amanchu_Main,P,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:23.74,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,初次的暑假中发生了很多初次经历的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.18,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:30.67,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,大家能友好相处真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:33.92,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,这是闪光的功劳？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:37.55,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,还是潜水的功劳？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:42.68,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,或许是夏日魔法的功劳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:46.95,Amanchu_Main,T,0,0,0,,伊豆现在正是夏日炎炎
